{"tid":2255230,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"難以置信，週末國家打吡我皇客勝仲有3.35倍","createTime":"2020-10-23T11:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T18:34:56.000Z","uid":44285,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"baef7918c2b4635817d9d7e48e96b0c324c113bb","tid":2255230,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T11:18:15.000Z","msg":"巴塞雖然早排歐聯大勝google隊，但有睇都知而家巴塞根本不成氣侯，食老本恰弱隊就ok，真係打大賽就碌柒。球王之前四場只入一球，居然同右閘沙治羅拔圖一樣。<br />\n<br />\n相反，雖然皇馬早排歐聯輸波，但落後三球僅輸一球，仲要差啲絕和。嚟緊皇馬都可以話贏硬。<br />\n<br />\n風水佬呃你十年八年，我一晚就可以幫大家上樓。"},{"pid":"c6a455d6d28d6e6d3528282cc58541c61b31dae1","tid":2255230,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T11:20:22.000Z","msg":"樓主精算師<br />\n我選擇信樓主"},{"pid":"a4c18b6429247690b458940ffedeba554816834b","tid":2255230,"uid":47783,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T11:20:39.000Z","msg":"牙積士今晚贏到皇馬 我表演針插龜頭<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1048325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1048325</a><br />\n<br />\n找數先ok？"},{"pid":"635b8fab43822bd65d0f56fa74f94091172b6e39","tid":2255230,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a4c18b6429247690b458940ffedeba554816834b","tid":2255230,"uid":47783,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T11:20:39.000Z","msg":"牙積士今晚贏到皇馬 我表演針插龜頭<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1048325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1048325</a><br />\n<br />\n找數先ok？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T11:32:04.000Z","msg":"大是大非當前就咪能25啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c654832289b6390af15e6426495d2c15352ca3c8","tid":2255230,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6a455d6d28d6e6d3528282cc58541c61b31dae1","tid":2255230,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T11:20:22.000Z","msg":"樓主精算師<br />\n我選擇信樓主"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T11:33:19.000Z","msg":"玩膠都有底線 你搵真嘢嚟講？